Package: threeBrain
Type: Package
Title: 3D Brain Visualization
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Zhengjia", "Wang", email = "zhengjia.wang@rice.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
    )
Description: This package is an html widget that uses WebGL engine called Three.js 
    to display brain surfaces on webpage interactively. It translates R objects 
    to JavaScript objects via JSON format. This package is mainly designed to 
    enhance AFNI/SUMA, and FreeSurfer and to provide a cross-platform 
    easy-to-share 3D viewer.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
